claim: The Magna Carta was written in 1500.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Magna Carta Libertatum  (  Medieval Latin for `` the Great Charter of the Liberties ''  )  , commonly called Magna Carta  (  also Magna Charta ; ''  (  the  )  Great Charter ''  )  , is a charter agreed to by King John of England at Runnymede , near Windsor , on 15 June 1215 .
